[22:01:51    14] The existing plan’s broad parser/printer redesign remains blocked by cJSON’s C-visible ownership layout, but the dispatch helper `parse_value` itself has no unsafe preconditions or raw-pointer handling. I’m narrowing this iteration to making that helper safe and containing its two legacy calls explicitly.
