[22:07:45     4]   checker's unsafe count. A full safe ownership redesign needs a separate
[22:07:45     4]   compatibility strategy for these public raw fields.
[22:07:45     4] - Keep any raw pointer use at the FFI/allocator boundary; the public `cJSON`
[22:07:45     4]   layout and allocation-hook ABI are compatibility constraints.
