[22:20:45    81] +1. Finish the printer cleanup: delete the now-disabled `legacy_print_object`
[22:20:45    81] +   and obsolete `print_with_format!` macro rather than leaving the old unsafe
[22:20:45    81] +   implementation in source.
[22:20:45    81] +2. Preserve the original observable allocator-hook sequence for
