[22:20:45    82] -  allocation/free ABI; replacing them with `memcpy` adds an unsafe-adjacent
[22:20:45    82] -  FFI import without making the allocation safe.
[22:20:45    82] -  Remaining instances include `print_string_ptr` and parser/printer traversal
[22:20:45    82] -  helpers.
[22:20:45    82] -  They all stem from the C-visible `cJSON` raw linked-node/string fields and
[22:20:45    82] -  hook-owned print/string allocations.
